entries.text: Market opened in consolidation pattern. Watching 5926 as key level.
CPI data came in below expectations. ES moving higher.
ES broke above 5926 with volume. Preparing to enter ES long.
Entered ES long at 5930, stop at 5905, target 5970.
AAPL breaking out of flag pattern. Entered long at 212.75.
ES reaching first target at 5945. Trailing stop to breakeven.
AAPL continuing higher with strong momentum.
ES hit target at 5970. Exited position for +40 points.
AAPL reached 218.50. Trimmed 50% of position per plan.
Market showing late-day strength. Holding remaining AAPL position overnight.

keyLessons: Plan execution was effective with precise entries
Trailing stops worked well in trending conditions
Scaling out partial positions preserved gains while capturing further upside

marketState: Bullish trend day with steady buying after positive CPI data
